BT /F2 18 Tf 50 746.00 Td (Holoscan Sensor Bridge 25G Presentation Speaker Notes) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 713.20 Td (Detailed slide-by-slide talk track and technical Q&A) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 686.40 Td (Prepared for presenting DFAE_Cert_ILT_2026_HSB.pptx to a technical audience.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 664.80 Td (Audience assumption: FPGA, embedded, networking, vision, and AI engineers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 643.20 Td (Presentation objective:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 621.60 Td (- Explain why Holoscan Sensor Bridge matters.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 610.80 Td (- Position Agilex 5 as the deterministic sensor-ingest and Ethernet-transport layer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 600.00 Td (- Explain how the NVIDIA host uses Holoscan for processing, visualization, and AI inference.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 589.20 Td (- Show what was actually brought up on AGX Thor.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 578.40 Td (- Be transparent about 10G/25G switching, MAX10 firmware, CoE behavior, and demo limitations.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 556.80 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 535.20 Td (Executive summary for presenter) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 508.40 Td (The presentation should land three main messages:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 486.80 Td (1. FPGA value:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 476.00 Td (   Agilex 5 handles real-world sensor interfaces, deterministic ingest, timing, protocol conversion,) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 465.20 Td (     packetization, and Ethernet transport.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 443.60 Td (2. NVIDIA Holoscan value:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 432.80 Td (   Holoscan provides the host-side graph framework for GPU accelerated processing, AI inference, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 422.00 Td (     visualization.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 400.40 Td (3. Demo proof:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 389.60 Td (   The 10GbE and 25GbE Agilex 5 Holoscan Sensor Bridge demos were both brought up on AGX Thor. 10G is the) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 378.80 Td (     simpler stable path. 25G works, but Thor requires boot-slot switching and the CoE interface refresh) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 368.00 Td (     workaround for repeated runs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 346.40 Td (Recommended verbal opener:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 324.80 Td (> Today I will walk through how Agilex 5 bridges high-bandwidth sensor data into NVIDIA Holoscan over Ethernet.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 314.00 Td (  The FPGA owns deterministic sensor capture and transport; the NVIDIA platform owns GPU processing, AI) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 303.20 Td (  inference, and visualization. I will cover the architecture, available reference designs, the demo setup, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 292.40 Td (  the practical bring-up lessons from both 10GbE and 25GbE on AGX Thor.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 270.80 Td (Recommended closing:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 249.20 Td (> The key takeaway is that this architecture gives customers a scalable path from custom sensors to GPU) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 238.40 Td (  processing over standard Ethernet. Altera provides the sensor-facing FPGA flexibility and deterministic) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 227.60 Td (  transport, while NVIDIA Holoscan provides the application and AI pipeline on the host.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 206.00 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 184.40 Td (Slide 1 - Holoscan Sensor Bridge 25G) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 157.60 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 133.80 Td (Introduce the topic and set the technical scope: Holoscan Sensor Bridge using 25GbE-capable Agilex 5 design) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 123.00 Td (  with NVIDIA host processing.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 101.40 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 77.60 Td (> This session is about the Holoscan Sensor Bridge 25G demo. We are connecting sensor data into NVIDIA Holoscan) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 66.80 Td (  using an Agilex 5 FPGA as the sensor-ingest and Ethernet-transport bridge. The demo focuses on MIPI camera) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 500 26 Td (Page 1 of 19) Tj ET
endstream
