BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 746.00 Td (Medical:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 724.40 Td (- Endoscopy, ultrasound, microscopy, surgical robotics, AI diagnostics.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 713.60 Td (- FPGA interfaces to specialized imaging sensors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 702.80 Td (- Holoscan handles visualization, enhancement, segmentation, inference.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 681.20 Td (Studio / broadcast:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 659.60 Td (- Low-latency video ingest, metadata, switching, effects.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 648.80 Td (- FPGA converts and aligns media streams.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 627.20 Td (Wireless:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 605.60 Td (- IQ/baseband data over JESD204 or custom RF paths.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 594.80 Td (- FPGA packetizes high-rate radio data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 584.00 Td (- Host analyzes, visualizes, or runs AI-assisted signal processing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 562.40 Td (Defense / aerospace:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 540.80 Td (- Radar, EO/IR, lidar, SIGINT.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 530.00 Td (- FPGA provides deterministic capture and transport.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 519.20 Td (- Host performs sensor fusion or target detection.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 497.60 Td (Key message) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 473.80 Td (> The same architecture repeats across markets: sensor diversity at the FPGA, compute scalability at the host.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 452.20 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 430.60 Td (Slide 7 - Available Today) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 403.80 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 380.00 Td (Show available reference designs and bandwidth options.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 358.40 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 334.60 Td (> Altera has multiple Holoscan-related sensor-to-Ethernet reference designs. For Agilex 5, the key designs are) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 323.80 Td (  the Group B 10GbE design and the Group A 25GbE design. These give customers a starting point depending on board) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 313.00 Td (  type, bandwidth, and number of streams.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 291.40 Td (Explain each design) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 267.60 Td (- Stratix 10 sensor processing kit: earlier HSB-related platform.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 256.80 Td (- Agilex 5 Group B 10GbE: simpler two-camera path.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 246.00 Td (- Agilex 5 Group A 25GbE: higher bandwidth, multi-stream, CoE-oriented path.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 224.40 Td (Customer guidance) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 200.60 Td (> If the customer wants a stable first evaluation, start with 10GbE. If the value proposition is bandwidth,) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 189.80 Td (  multi-stream scaling, or 25G transport, use the Group A 25GbE design.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 168.20 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 146.60 Td (Slide 8 - Step by Step Guide) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 119.80 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 96.00 Td (Guide field teams on qualifying customer opportunities.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 74.40 Td (What to say) Tj ET
