BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 746.00 Td (> This is a discovery workflow for customer engagement. Start by identifying customers using GPUs for edge AI) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 735.20 Td (  or high-rate sensor processing. Then understand the sensors, protocols, bandwidth, and AI throughput) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 724.40 Td (  requirement. Finally, map that to an Altera reference design.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 702.80 Td (Discovery questions) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 679.00 Td (- Which GPU or host platform is used?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 668.20 Td (- Which sensors are used?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 657.40 Td (- What are the sensor interfaces?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 646.60 Td (- How many streams?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 635.80 Td (- What resolution and frame rate?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 625.00 Td (- What latency budget?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 614.20 Td (- What Ethernet speed is required?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 603.40 Td (- Is FPGA preprocessing needed?) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 592.60 Td (- Does the customer need deterministic trigger/sync?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 571.00 Td (Technical framing) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 547.20 Td (> The right design is chosen from the data rate and system architecture, not just from the camera type.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 525.60 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 504.00 Td (Slide 9 - Altera FPGA Developer Site) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 477.20 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 453.40 Td (Point audience to customer-facing collateral.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 431.80 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 408.00 Td (> The Altera FPGA Developer Site is the first stop for customers. It provides reference design descriptions,) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 397.20 Td (  supported hardware, Quartus version requirements, and links to GitHub documentation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 375.60 Td (Why it matters) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 351.80 Td (- Reduces risk of using wrong branch or wrong SOF.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 341.00 Td (- Provides official README flow.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 330.20 Td (- Links to design collateral and prebuilt images.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 308.60 Td (Practical tip) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 284.80 Td (> Always verify the exact FPGA board group and Quartus version before programming a design.) Tj ET
