BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 472.80 Td (Customer positioning) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 449.00 Td (> This supports both evaluation and engineering adoption. Use prebuilt binaries for demo, then use source for) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 438.20 Td (  customization.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 416.60 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
