BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 322.80 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 299.00 Td (> Now we move from architecture to the actual demo. The demo has three major parts: programming the FPGA,) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 288.20 Td (  configuring the AGX Thor host, and running Holoscan applications.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 266.60 Td (Transition) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 242.80 Td (> I will first cover hardware requirements and connections, then software setup and commands.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 221.20 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
