BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 531.20 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 507.40 Td (> On the host, we need JetPack, the Holoscan Sensor Bridge repository, Docker, and Holoscan dependencies. On) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 496.60 Td (  the FPGA side, we need Quartus Programmer 26.1 to program the SOF or JIC.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 475.00 Td (Important details) Tj ET
