BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 440.40 Td (- HSB Docker build used --igpu for AGX Thor.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 429.60 Td (- Quartus Programmer is required for FPGA and MAX10 updates.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 408.00 Td (Verbal correction if slide is generic) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 384.20 Td (> For AGX Thor, use the iGPU Docker build path. Use dGPU only on a host with a discrete NVIDIA GPU.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 362.60 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 341.00 Td (Slide 15 - Development Kit and Host System Connection Diagram) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 314.20 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 290.40 Td (Explain physical data/control connections.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 268.80 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 245.00 Td (> Sensor data enters the Agilex board through MIPI. The FPGA formats and packetizes the stream, then sends it) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 234.20 Td (  over Ethernet through the SFP connector to the NVIDIA host. The host also sends control transactions, such as) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 223.40 Td (  camera I2C configuration, through the HSB path.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 201.80 Td (Debug logic) Tj ET
