BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 156.40 Td (- If hololink-enumerate fails: check HSB endpoint/network.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 145.60 Td (- If camera I2C fails but enumerate works: check MIPI power, MAX10, cable, camera.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 124.00 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 102.40 Td (Slide 16 - Modular Development Kit Connector) Tj ET
