BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 746.00 Td (Highlight connector and switch importance.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 724.40 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 700.60 Td (> The MDK connector details matter. During bring-up we found that early production MDKs may have a MAX10) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 689.80 Td (  firmware issue where MIPI connector power is not enabled. That causes camera I2C failures even though the FPGA) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 679.00 Td (  and Ethernet path are working.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 657.40 Td (MAX10 fix) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 633.60 Td (Explain:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 612.00 Td (1. Set SW4 to ON to put MAX10 on the JTAG chain.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 601.20 Td (2. Reflash MAX10 with max10_top_rtl_v1p1p6_fw_v2p0p1.pof.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 590.40 Td (3. Power off the board.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 579.60 Td (4. Set SW4 back to OFF so FPGA appears on JTAG again.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 558.00 Td (Key message) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 534.20 Td (> Camera I2C failure is not always software. On early MDKs, it can be missing MIPI connector power due to MAX10) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 523.40 Td (  firmware.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 501.80 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 480.20 Td (Slide 17 - Run Applications) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 453.40 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 429.60 Td (Explain high-level execution flow.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 408.00 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 384.20 Td (> There are two sides to running the demo: program the Agilex FPGA and run the Holoscan application on the) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 373.40 Td (  NVIDIA host.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 351.80 Td (FPGA side) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 328.00 Td (- Program .sof through JTAG for volatile demo.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 317.20 Td (- Program .jic to flash for non-volatile boot.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 295.60 Td (Host side) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 271.80 Td (For AGX Thor:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.5 Tf 50 250.20 Td (sh docker/build.sh --igpu) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.5 Tf 50 241.10 Td (sh docker/demo.sh) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 221.20 Td (Then run a camera app.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 199.60 Td (Correct customer demo command) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 175.80 Td (For two cameras in 25G CoE mode:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.5 Tf 50 154.20 Td (python3 examples/agx5_multiviewer.py --cam 2 --lines 2160 --frame-rate 30 --receiver-type coe) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 134.30 Td (Note) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 110.50 Td (The slide may show --cam 8; explain that --cam 8 is for eight logical streams. With two physical cameras, use) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 99.70 Td (  --cam 2.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 78.10 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 500 26 Td (Page 9 of 19) Tj ET
