BT /F2 13 Tf 50 746.00 Td (Slide 18 - Hardware) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 719.20 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 695.40 Td (Transition into FPGA architecture.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 673.80 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 650.00 Td (> Now let's look inside the FPGA design to understand how the raw camera data becomes Ethernet packets for the) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 639.20 Td (  Holoscan host.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 617.60 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 596.00 Td (Slide 19 - The Design) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 569.20 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 545.40 Td (Show high-level FPGA block diagram.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 523.80 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 500.00 Td (> The design starts with two MIPI camera inputs. Agilex 5 receives the MIPI data, converts it into streaming) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 489.20 Td (  video, packs it into the format expected by HSB software, routes it into the HSB IP, and sends it to the host) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 478.40 Td (  over Ethernet.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 456.80 Td (Technical breakdown) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 433.00 Td (- IMX678 cameras provide MIPI CSI data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 422.20 Td (- MIPI D-PHY receives physical lanes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 411.40 Td (- CSI-2 IP converts to internal stream.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 400.60 Td (- VVP/broadcast logic packs/replicates data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 389.80 Td (- HSB IP packetizes and controls transport.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 379.00 Td (- GTS Ethernet sends data to Thor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 357.40 Td (Key message) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 333.60 Td (> Altera logic wraps and adapts around NVIDIA HSB IP to make it usable with Agilex hardware and Altera Ethernet) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 322.80 Td (  IP.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 301.20 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 50 279.60 Td (Slide 20 - Architecture Overview) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 252.80 Td (Purpose of the slide) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 229.00 Td (Explain the Platform Designer subsystem structure.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 207.40 Td (What to say) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 183.60 Td (> The design is made of four major subsystems: MIPI ingest, VVP broadcast and packing, HSB subsystem, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 172.80 Td (  Ethernet subsystem.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10.5 Tf 50 151.20 Td (Subsystem details) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 127.40 Td (1. MIPI subsystem:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 116.60 Td (   Receives physical camera streams using MIPI D-PHY and CSI-2 IP.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 95.00 Td (2. Broadcast/packing subsystem:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 84.20 Td (   Converts Altera Streaming Video Protocol into tightly packed CSI-style data expected by host software.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8.8 Tf 50 62.60 Td (3. HSB subsystem:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 500 26 Td (Page 10 of 19) Tj ET
